description: KeePassHttp is a plugin for KeePass 2.x and provides a means of exposing password entries securely (256bit AES/CBC) over HTTP. This plugin is primarily intended for use with PassIFox for Mozilla Firefox and chromeIPass for Google Chrome.
summary: KeePass 2 plugin to to expose password entries securely (256bit AES/CBC) over HTTP
author: Perry Nguyen, Lukas Schulze
